long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Log from PHP to a Browser Developer Tools FirePHP Console Panel via HTTP Response Headers.

Supported protocols:

- FirePHP (Wildfire based)
- Chrome Logger

For a list of supported server libraries see http://firephp.org
